sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant G as Gmail
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant DB as Neon
    participant B as Next batch

    G->>API: GET /c?a=ID&sig=HMAC
    API->>API: verify HMAC + UA
    alt valid
        API->>DB: INSERT clicks
        API->>U: 302 redirect
    else invalid
        API->>U: 302 redirect only
    end
    B->>DB: compute centroid
    B->>B: rank by similarity